# MotionGuard â€“ Motion Detection Robot

## Description
**MotionGuard** is a security robot that detects motion in designated areas and alerts users. It enhances home or office safety with a smart, automated monitoring system.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- PIR Motion Sensors  
- Raspberry Pi  
- Python  

## Key Features
- Real-time motion detection  
- Alert notifications  
- Portable security system  

## My Role
Integrated sensors, programmed detection and alert logic, and conducted system testing.

